+ *   7 - TLS segment #2			[ Wine's %fs Win32 segment ]
+ *   8 - TLS segment #3
+ *   9 - reserved
+ *  10 - reserved
+ *  11 - reserved
+ *
+ *  ------- start of kernel segments:
+ *
+ *  12 - kernel code segment		<==== new cacheline
+ *  13 - kernel data segment
+ *  14 - default user CS
